WEBVTT

00:04:58.640 --> 00:05:01.542
ameriški način gradnje mest

00:05:01.542 --> 00:05:04.253
je kakovostne javne prostore

00:05:04.253 --> 00:05:06.237
v mnogih mestih

00:05:06.237 --> 00:05:07.992
skoraj izničil,

00:05:07.992 --> 00:05:09.989
zaradi tega pa je prišlo

00:05:09.989 --> 00:05:12.544
do upada odnosov,

00:05:12.544 --> 00:05:14.748
stvari, ki nas osrečujejo.

00:05:14.748 --> 00:05:16.795
Mnoge študije kažejo na rast

00:05:16.795 --> 00:05:21.486
samote in upad solidarnosti,

00:05:21.486 --> 00:05:26.142
poštenja ter družbene 
in civilne participacije.

00:05:26.142 --> 00:05:29.506
Kako naj potem zgradimo mesta,

00:05:29.506 --> 00:05:32.116
v katerih nam bo mar?